OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772791513
OL,3,CPrivate company wins second tender to
OL,4,Crun popular lido
OL,6,FFirst Point Property Services,
OL,7,Foperating under the name 'Lido
OL,8,FJersey', will run the island's popular
OL,9,FHavre des Pas Bathing Pool after
OL,10,Fwinning the tender for a second time.
OL,12,FThey were initially chosen in October,
OL,13,Fbut that decision was thrown out after
OL,14,Fan independent review found the
OL,15,Foriginal process was flawed.
OL,17,FThe community group 'Love Our Lido'
OL,18,Fwanted to run the facility, but
OL,19,Fultimately pulled out of the reopened
OL,20,Ftender over funding concerns.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
