FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772791513
OL,3,CPrivate company wins second tender to
OL,4,Crun popular lido
OL,6,FJersey Business were appointed by the
OL,7,FInfrastructure Minister, Deputy Andy
OL,8,FJehan, to independently oversee the
OL,9,Fsecond process.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the group says:
OL,12,F"Following a competitive and
OL,13,Fcomprehensive tender process, Lido
OL,14,FJersey has completed the agreement of
OL,15,Flease terms for the pool and
OL,16,Ffacilities at Havre des Pas."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772791513
OL,3,CPrivate company wins second tender to
OL,4,Crun popular lido
OL,6,FThe site will be leased from Jersey
OL,7,FProperty Holdings, the Government's
OL,8,Fcorporate landlord, although the
OL,9,Flength of the contract has not been
OL,10,Fannounced - a nine-year deal was
OL,11,Fproposed under the first tender.
OL,13,FJersey Business adds: "First Point
OL,14,FProperty Services will assume
OL,15,Fresponsibility for the full management
OL,16,Fand maintenance of the site, including
OL,17,Fthe swimming pool on 1 April 2026."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
