FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772791513
OL,3,CPrivate company wins second tender to
OL,4,Crun popular lido
OL,6,FSt Clement Constable Marcus Troy is
OL,7,Fthe Director of the successful bidder
OL,8,Fand says: "This marks the beginning of
OL,9,Fan exciting new chapter for the Lido.
OL,10,FWe look forward to sharing our
OL,11,Fcommunity-focused vision and plans for
OL,12,Fthe site in the coming weeks."
OL,14,FMeanwhile, outgoing tenant Marcus
OL,15,FCalvani, from The Lido (Havre des Pas)
OL,16,FLimited, explains: "We are immensely
OL,17,Fproud of the foundations that have
OL,18,Fbeen laid and are encouraged that
OL,19,Fothers recognise and will take forward
OL,20,Fthe strength and value that's been
OL,21,Fcreated.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
