OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772791513
OL,3,CPrivate company wins second tender to
OL,4,Crun popular lido
OL,6,F"We sincerely wish Lido Jersey every
OL,7,Fsuccess in their future endeavours and
OL,8,Flook forward to seeing how this
OL,9,Fimportant St Helier landmark develops
OL,10,Fin the years ahead."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
